WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 23=

00:01:50.930 --> 00:01:52.180 line:80%
I've never understood

00:01:53.900 --> 00:01:56.060 line:80%
why the Man in Black

00:01:56.980 --> 00:01:58.540 line:80%
set ambushes everywhere and

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:00.290 line:80%
chased us all the way
since Chang Fort.

00:02:01.490 --> 00:02:02.700 line:80%
Just now, I got it.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:04.490 line:80%
Nie Zhe and the Man in Black

00:02:04.490 --> 00:02:06.340 line:80%
are both so obsessed with
the Jade Sunflower.

00:02:06.820 --> 00:02:08.650 line:80%
You lured me into going to Chang Fort,

00:02:09.020 --> 00:02:11.460 line:80%
then tricked me into
seeking the Shi brothers.

00:02:11.930 --> 00:02:13.650 line:80%
Also for the Jade Sunflower.

00:02:15.210 --> 00:02:16.300 line:80%
And Lu Chengnan

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:17.620 line:80%
betrayed his master and sect

00:02:18.140 --> 00:02:19.690 line:80%
just to take it.

00:02:21.020 --> 00:02:23.210 line:80%
Guess the Jade Sunflower, like saliva,

00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:26.090 line:80%
is an important medium
for cultivating the Ziwei Method.

00:02:29.460 --> 00:02:31.020 line:80%
I knew I couldn't hide it from you.

00:02:34.210 --> 00:02:36.210 line:80%
I once suspected
your sudden surge in power

00:02:36.210 --> 00:02:37.970 line:80%
came from cultivating the Ziwei Method.

00:02:38.930 --> 00:02:40.410 line:80%
But on the way back
from the Snow Mountain,

00:02:40.780 --> 00:02:41.810 line:80%
I have already checked that

00:02:42.580 --> 00:02:43.810 line:80%
the saliva hasn't decreased.

00:02:44.210 --> 00:02:45.780 line:80%
If you've been
cultivating the Ziwei Method,

00:02:46.060 --> 00:02:47.740 line:80%
then where did your saliva come from?

00:02:48.300 --> 00:02:49.490 line:80%
When did you tamper with it?

00:02:49.970 --> 00:02:51.090 line:80%
What else are you hiding from me?

00:02:51.090 --> 00:02:51.970 line:80%
Zhao.

00:02:52.740 --> 00:02:54.620 line:80%
I got the saliva purely by accident.

00:03:04.460 --> 00:03:05.580 line:80%
It actually worked.

00:03:06.780 --> 00:03:08.410 line:80%
This wasn't my intention.

00:03:11.740 --> 00:03:13.490 line:80%
You really are
cultivating the Ziwei Method.

00:03:15.140 --> 00:03:16.300 line:80%
If you insist,

00:03:17.340 --> 00:03:18.340 line:80%
I'll never let you

00:03:18.340 --> 00:03:19.340 line:80%
get the Jade Sunflower.

00:03:19.970 --> 00:03:20.810 line:80%
Zhao.

00:03:28.300 --> 00:03:29.140 line:80%
Where is she?

00:03:30.060 --> 00:03:30.900 line:80%
Search!

00:03:41.460 --> 00:03:42.810 line:80%
Zhao, look.

00:03:42.810 --> 00:03:45.020 line:80%
The persimmon cakes
we sent to Luoying Valley years ago

00:03:45.020 --> 00:03:46.490 line:80%
were picked from this tree.

00:03:48.970 --> 00:03:50.490 line:80%
So you really are Shi Tieqiao.

00:03:50.490 --> 00:03:52.020 line:80%
(Shi brothers, Shi Tieqiao)
Uncle Tieqiao.

00:03:52.020 --> 00:03:53.370 line:80%
I never dreamed

00:03:54.060 --> 00:03:54.900 line:80%
I'd see Zhao

00:03:55.060 --> 00:03:55.930 line:80%
in my lifetime.

00:03:56.900 --> 00:03:58.090 line:80%
You look more like your mother,

00:03:58.780 --> 00:03:59.620 line:80%
but your eyes

00:04:00.460 --> 00:04:01.410 line:80%
take after your aunt.

00:04:03.750 --> 00:04:05.370 line:80%
This place is so similar to
Luoying Valley.

00:04:06.210 --> 00:04:07.970 line:80%
What a wonderful retreat.

00:04:08.580 --> 00:04:10.020 line:80%
No wonder we couldn't find it.

00:04:11.810 --> 00:04:12.900 line:80%
It's surrounded by mountains.

00:04:13.300 --> 00:04:14.180 line:80%
Warm air creates mist.

00:04:14.810 --> 00:04:15.650 line:80%
Mountains hidden in fog.

00:04:15.940 --> 00:04:17.380 line:80%
Truly hard to track.

00:04:19.530 --> 00:04:20.370 line:80%
Just put it there.

00:04:21.900 --> 00:04:23.050 line:80%
Others can retreat

00:04:23.050 --> 00:04:25.210 line:80%
with their small families,

00:04:25.210 --> 00:04:27.900 line:80%
but ours has always been a big clan.

00:04:27.900 --> 00:04:30.970 line:80%
All those aunts and uncles.

00:04:30.970 --> 00:04:32.940 line:80%
Including your second uncle
and fourth great-uncle.

00:04:32.940 --> 00:04:34.610 line:80%
Over a hundred people total.

00:04:34.610 --> 00:04:37.340 line:80%
If your aunt hadn't found this place,

00:04:37.340 --> 00:04:38.730 line:80%
we could never have retreated

00:04:38.730 --> 00:04:39.780 line:80%
even if we wanted to.

00:04:41.500 --> 00:04:42.460 line:80%
You two youngsters

00:04:43.170 --> 00:04:44.780 line:80%
went to such trouble to lure me out.

00:04:45.210 --> 00:04:46.460 line:80%
What's this all about?

00:04:55.410 --> 00:04:56.410 line:80%
Thank you, Uncle Tieqiao.

00:04:58.940 --> 00:05:00.530 line:80%
Lu Chengnan's tomb

00:05:00.530 --> 00:05:02.140 line:80%
was indeed built by us brothers.

00:05:03.170 --> 00:05:05.700 line:80%
But that pillar

00:05:05.700 --> 00:05:07.820 line:80%
must have been added later by Haosheng.

00:05:07.820 --> 00:05:09.700 line:80%
Haosheng admired Lu Chengnan's character

00:05:09.700 --> 00:05:11.700 line:80%
but couldn't erect a monument openly.

00:05:12.780 --> 00:05:13.620 line:80%
So

00:05:13.850 --> 00:05:15.090 line:80%
he built this pillar,

00:05:17.210 --> 00:05:18.780 line:80%
but it ruined our design.

00:05:20.650 --> 00:05:21.780 line:80%
Uncle Chang meant well.

00:05:22.880 --> 00:05:23.730 line:80%
Well, he...

00:05:23.730 --> 00:05:25.380 line:80%
Died because of that act of kindness.

00:05:26.210 --> 00:05:27.210 line:80%
Uncle Tieqiao, do you know

00:05:29.050 --> 00:05:31.290 line:80%
about the massacre
of Uncle Chang's clan?

00:05:31.580 --> 00:05:32.730 line:80%
Of course I do.

00:05:32.730 --> 00:05:33.730 line:80%
As his brother,

00:05:35.380 --> 00:05:36.700 line:80%
why did you do nothing?

00:05:42.340 --> 00:05:43.730 line:80%
Back when we left.

00:05:44.460 --> 00:05:46.290 line:80%
Pingshu repeatedly told us

00:05:47.140 --> 00:05:47.980 line:80%
to leave

00:05:48.290 --> 00:05:49.610 line:80%
completely.

00:05:49.900 --> 00:05:50.850 line:80%
Step away from Jianghu

00:05:51.530 --> 00:05:53.050 line:80%
means no half-measures.

00:05:53.530 --> 00:05:55.900 line:80%
No matter
if Jianghu sees endless battles

00:05:56.650 --> 00:05:58.090 line:80%
or a bloodbath,

00:05:58.460 --> 00:06:01.410 line:80%
it has nothing to do with you.

00:06:02.460 --> 00:06:03.300 line:80%
In fact, back then,

00:06:03.700 --> 00:06:06.290 line:80%
your aunt also advised Haosheng.

00:06:07.780 --> 00:06:08.970 line:80%
Either recruit followers

00:06:09.290 --> 00:06:10.820 line:80%
to avoid being easily destroyed,

00:06:11.210 --> 00:06:12.050 line:80%
or

00:06:12.780 --> 00:06:13.970 line:80%
like me,

00:06:14.380 --> 00:06:16.340 line:80%
retreat to the mountains resolutely.

00:06:16.940 --> 00:06:17.820 line:80%
The worst

00:06:18.290 --> 00:06:19.700 line:80%
is being half-retired

00:06:20.700 --> 00:06:21.610 line:80%
like Haosheng.

00:06:22.460 --> 00:06:23.460 line:80%
Ms. Cai

00:06:23.820 --> 00:06:24.730 line:80%
truly has insight.

00:06:25.380 --> 00:06:26.460 line:80%
Over the past ten years,

00:06:27.380 --> 00:06:29.650 line:80%
the brave elders of the Chang clan

00:06:29.650 --> 00:06:30.850 line:80%
have either aged, fallen ill,

00:06:31.940 --> 00:06:33.020 line:80%
or passed away.

00:06:33.610 --> 00:06:35.460 line:80%
Chang Fort lost its ability
to defend itself long ago.

00:06:36.090 --> 00:06:38.700 line:80%
But Uncle Chang still
went down the mountain often

00:06:39.340 --> 00:06:41.140 line:80%
to get involved in Jianghu affairs.

00:06:46.290 --> 00:06:47.970 line:80%
He couldn't let us go.

00:06:49.410 --> 00:06:50.380 line:80%
Staying or leaving

00:06:51.340 --> 00:06:52.730 line:80%
was our choice.

00:06:53.020 --> 00:06:54.050 line:80%
It has nothing to do with you.

00:06:54.820 --> 00:06:55.660 line:80%
No need to feel guilty.

00:06:56.700 --> 00:06:57.540 line:80%
However,

00:06:57.730 --> 00:06:58.900 line:80%
Chang clan's mechanism

00:06:59.290 --> 00:07:00.940 line:80%
changes its formation core
every three years.

00:07:02.700 --> 00:07:04.610 line:80%
Without a familiar guide,

00:07:05.090 --> 00:07:06.900 line:80%
outsiders can't enter.

00:07:07.820 --> 00:07:09.020 line:80%
Who would have thought...

00:07:09.780 --> 00:07:10.620 line:80%
Uncle Tieqiao,

00:07:11.580 --> 00:07:13.780 line:80%
where is the Jade Sunflower

00:07:13.780 --> 00:07:14.620 line:80%
Lu Chengnan took out?

00:07:16.650 --> 00:07:17.730 line:80%
Jade Sunflower?

00:07:19.870 --> 00:07:20.730 line:80%
What's wrong with you?

00:07:20.730 --> 00:07:21.570 line:80%
Mu.

00:07:56.090 --> 00:07:56.930 line:80%
You're awake.

00:08:06.380 --> 00:08:07.850 line:80%
Your pulse is finally back to normal.

00:08:08.820 --> 00:08:09.660 line:80%
You know,

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:11.460 line:80%
when I was little,
I was also in poor health,

00:08:11.840 --> 00:08:12.780 line:80%
often had high fevers.

00:08:13.460 --> 00:08:14.580 line:80%
But I'd cry and fuss,

00:08:14.850 --> 00:08:16.020 line:80%
and talk nonsense.

00:08:16.340 --> 00:08:18.050 line:80%
Wanted the whole Luoying Valley to know.

00:08:18.050 --> 00:08:19.340 line:80%
That way, Uncle Douhua and others would

00:08:19.340 --> 00:08:21.020 line:80%
bring me lots of snacks and drinks.

00:08:21.940 --> 00:08:23.050 line:80%
Not like you.

00:08:23.850 --> 00:08:26.210 line:80%
Burning up all night without a sound.

00:08:26.210 --> 00:08:27.290 line:80%
You're quite tough.

00:08:28.210 --> 00:08:30.340 line:80%
I got used to this before I was five.

00:08:30.610 --> 00:08:32.690 line:80%
Crying or fussing,

00:08:32.930 --> 00:08:34.290 line:80%
someone has to care.

00:08:35.450 --> 00:08:36.620 line:80%
If no one cares,

00:08:37.410 --> 00:08:38.620 line:80%
what's the point?

00:08:39.650 --> 00:08:40.490 line:80%
Besides,

00:08:40.900 --> 00:08:42.290 line:80%
we all die eventually.

00:08:44.930 --> 00:08:46.290 line:80%
When did the poison strike?

00:08:46.790 --> 00:08:47.630 line:80%
Why didn't you tell me

00:08:47.640 --> 00:08:48.900 line:80%
something so important?

00:08:48.900 --> 00:08:50.810 line:80%
Would it make any difference?

00:08:51.530 --> 00:08:53.650 line:80%
I shouldn't even exist.

00:08:55.780 --> 00:08:56.620 line:80%
Except for my father.

00:08:58.140 --> 00:08:59.740 line:80%
Everyone wishes me gone.

00:09:06.380 --> 00:09:07.290 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:09:08.780 --> 00:09:10.930 line:80%
I have my father's Innate Circulation,

00:09:10.930 --> 00:09:12.900 line:80%
plus the medicine
you went through so much trouble

00:09:12.900 --> 00:09:15.020 line:80%
to bring me from the Hanhai Mountains.

00:09:15.020 --> 00:09:16.330 line:80%
I won't die anytime soon.

00:09:17.650 --> 00:09:18.930 line:80%
Won't die.

00:09:19.380 --> 00:09:20.740 line:80%
Do you know your pulse almost stopped

00:09:20.740 --> 00:09:22.100 line:80%
when the poison struck last night?

00:09:28.930 --> 00:09:29.770 line:80%
Zhao,

00:09:31.650 --> 00:09:32.740 line:80%
I made you worry again.

00:09:33.980 --> 00:09:34.820 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:09:35.530 --> 00:09:36.500 line:80%
But truly, I'm fine,

00:09:37.100 --> 00:09:38.450 line:80%
I haven't found the Man in Black,

00:09:39.620 --> 00:09:40.690 line:80%
haven't avenged the Chang clan,

00:09:41.220 --> 00:09:42.380 line:80%
haven't avenged my father.

00:09:42.380 --> 00:09:43.220 line:80%
Avenge, avenge.

00:09:43.570 --> 00:09:44.530 line:80%
If the poison strikes,

00:09:44.530 --> 00:09:45.610 line:80%
- you'll do nothing.
- If that day comes,

00:09:46.810 --> 00:09:47.650 line:80%
forget me,

00:09:48.980 --> 00:09:50.500 line:80%
and continue as Miss Cai,

00:09:52.380 --> 00:09:53.380 line:80%
Manager Cai.

00:09:58.860 --> 00:09:59.700 line:80%
Don't speak nonsense.

00:10:02.530 --> 00:10:05.020 line:80%
This is Uncle Tieqiao's
secret detox soup.

00:10:05.020 --> 00:10:06.500 line:80%
It can even suppress corpse poison.

00:10:06.500 --> 00:10:07.650 line:80%
Drink it. You won't die from it.

00:10:14.930 --> 00:10:15.980 line:80%
Alright.

00:10:31.620 --> 00:10:32.570 line:80%
What's the matter?

00:10:32.570 --> 00:10:33.650 line:80%
Not feeling well again?

00:10:35.780 --> 00:10:36.620 line:80%
It's so bitter.

00:10:37.050 --> 00:10:38.290 line:80%
I crave some Smileys.

00:10:50.380 --> 00:10:51.860 line:80%
I didn't make you get poisoned.

00:10:52.140 --> 00:10:53.620 line:80%
Why should I make you food?

00:11:01.900 --> 00:11:02.740 line:80%
Uncle Tiefeng?

00:11:02.900 --> 00:11:05.260 line:80%
(Shi brothers, Shi Tiefeng)

00:11:05.290 --> 00:11:06.130 line:80%
Zhao!

00:11:09.780 --> 00:11:11.220 line:80%
What delicious food are you making?

00:11:11.220 --> 00:11:12.060 line:80%
It smells amazing.

00:11:13.810 --> 00:11:14.650 line:80%
Smiley.

00:11:16.050 --> 00:11:17.690 line:80%
Pingshu made it once years ago.

00:11:17.690 --> 00:11:19.620 line:80%
Haosheng and the others ate it all.

00:11:19.620 --> 00:11:21.380 line:80%
I didn't get any!

00:11:21.380 --> 00:11:22.530 line:80%
Quick, give me some.

00:11:27.530 --> 00:11:28.500 line:80%
Uncle Tiefeng, help yourself.

00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:29.650 line:80%
Just leave one piece for my friend.

00:11:30.220 --> 00:11:31.060 line:80%
Friend?

00:11:32.020 --> 00:11:33.570 line:80%
You mean that Mu, right?

00:11:34.170 --> 00:11:35.330 line:80%
I heard from Tieqiao.

00:11:35.330 --> 00:11:37.410 line:80%
He said Mu is quite good-looking.

00:11:38.050 --> 00:11:39.050 line:80%
Is he your sweetheart?

00:11:43.220 --> 00:11:44.140 line:80%
How could that be?

00:11:44.620 --> 00:11:46.220 line:80%
What's there to be shy about?

00:11:46.530 --> 00:11:47.860 line:80%
You're talented and he's handsome.

00:11:48.020 --> 00:11:49.290 line:80%
You're a perfect match.

00:11:49.290 --> 00:11:51.020 line:80%
Though he's from the demon sect,

00:11:51.020 --> 00:11:52.780 line:80%
not all demon sect members are bad.

00:11:52.780 --> 00:11:54.570 line:80%
The one who helped us
get the Jade Sunflower

00:11:54.570 --> 00:11:55.570 line:80%
to heal

00:11:55.570 --> 00:11:56.500 line:80%
was also the demon sect...

00:11:59.690 --> 00:12:01.810 line:80%
Do you mean aunt's friend,

00:12:02.220 --> 00:12:03.290 line:80%
the masked one?

00:12:04.500 --> 00:12:06.100 line:80%
So tasty, truly delicious.

00:12:06.450 --> 00:12:07.290 line:80%
I just remembered

00:12:07.290 --> 00:12:08.170 line:80%
I have something to do.

00:12:12.220 --> 00:12:13.060 line:80%
Uncle Tiefeng!

00:12:16.580 --> 00:12:19.820 line:80%
(Kind and Hospitable)

00:12:23.650 --> 00:12:24.490 line:80%
Zhizhen.

00:12:25.170 --> 00:12:27.620 line:80%
Look, what has your son done?

00:12:27.620 --> 00:12:29.220 line:80%
Luckily Pingchun hasn't arrived.

00:12:29.220 --> 00:12:30.290 line:80%
If he had come,

00:12:30.290 --> 00:12:31.620 line:80%
he'd definitely fight you.

00:12:34.380 --> 00:12:35.780 line:80%
I failed to teach my son well.

00:12:36.630 --> 00:12:37.820 line:80%
I'm sorry about Pingchun,

00:12:38.250 --> 00:12:39.290 line:80%
and Zhao.

00:12:39.810 --> 00:12:41.320 line:80%
When I get back to Peiqiong Manor,

00:12:41.790 --> 00:12:43.050 line:80%
I'll break that boy's legs.

00:12:43.050 --> 00:12:44.980 line:80%
What good will breaking his legs do?

00:12:44.980 --> 00:12:46.290 line:80%
Do you want Zhao

00:12:47.050 --> 00:12:47.930 line:80%
to marry a cripple?

00:12:49.500 --> 00:12:50.410 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:12:51.100 --> 00:12:53.620 line:80%
I have a way to fix this.

00:12:54.100 --> 00:12:55.900 line:80%
Your son refuses the marriage,
doesn't he?

00:12:56.380 --> 00:12:57.450 line:80%
My son does.

00:12:58.100 --> 00:13:00.740 line:80%
I think Yuzhi and Zhao
are a great match.

00:13:02.410 --> 00:13:03.500 line:80%
Song Shijun.

00:13:03.500 --> 00:13:04.620 line:80%
Had this in mind all along?

00:13:05.620 --> 00:13:07.500 line:80%
I wondered why you're so eager.

00:13:07.500 --> 00:13:09.410 line:80%
What does Yuqi and Zhao's marriage

00:13:09.410 --> 00:13:10.570 line:80%
have to do with the Guangtian Sect?

00:13:10.810 --> 00:13:12.220 line:80%
- Yet you ran faster than me.
- This...

00:13:12.220 --> 00:13:13.290 line:80%
What are you talking about?

00:13:13.290 --> 00:13:14.690 line:80%
The Six Sects are united.

00:13:14.690 --> 00:13:16.330 line:80%
How can it be unrelated to
the Guangtian Sect?

00:13:16.330 --> 00:13:17.900 line:80%
I care about the younger generation.

00:13:17.900 --> 00:13:19.290 line:80%
Enough. I'm not arguing with you.

00:13:19.780 --> 00:13:20.860 line:80%
I just want to remind you

00:13:21.740 --> 00:13:24.020 line:80%
Yuzhi and Lingbo are already engaged.

00:13:24.020 --> 00:13:24.860 line:80%
Father.

00:13:27.100 --> 00:13:27.940 line:80%
Father.

00:13:29.410 --> 00:13:30.250 line:80%
Father.

00:13:30.420 --> 00:13:32.050 line:80%
I want to withdraw my engagement
to Song Yuzhi.

00:13:36.460 --> 00:13:37.320 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:13:37.320 --> 00:13:38.980 line:80%
Are you serious?

00:13:42.520 --> 00:13:43.530 line:80%
Father, please grant my wish.

00:13:49.030 --> 00:13:49.890 line:80%
Grant it.

00:13:49.900 --> 00:13:50.900 line:80%
Definitely.

00:13:52.620 --> 00:13:53.570 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:13:53.570 --> 00:13:55.020 line:80%
You've finally come to your senses.

00:13:55.020 --> 00:13:56.410 line:80%
That rascal Yuzhi

00:13:56.410 --> 00:13:57.810 line:80%
is not worthy of you.

00:13:59.020 --> 00:14:00.410 line:80%
I also think he's not worthy.

00:14:00.900 --> 00:14:02.650 line:80%
I was blinded by the engagement before,

00:14:02.650 --> 00:14:03.980 line:80%
but now I see clearly.

00:14:03.980 --> 00:14:04.820 line:80%
He's

00:14:05.220 --> 00:14:06.780 line:80%
cold and unfeeling,

00:14:07.290 --> 00:14:08.290 line:80%
stubborn and dull,

00:14:09.050 --> 00:14:10.100 line:80%
narrow-minded,

00:14:10.830 --> 00:14:11.900 line:80%
and lacks any sense of romance.

00:14:13.290 --> 00:14:14.330 line:80%
He's truly not worthy of me.

00:14:15.290 --> 00:14:16.320 line:80%
My future husband

00:14:17.140 --> 00:14:18.290 line:80%
should cherish,

00:14:18.810 --> 00:14:19.650 line:80%
understand,

00:14:19.860 --> 00:14:20.700 line:80%
and protect me.

00:14:21.020 --> 00:14:22.930 line:80%
Even a relationship
like Zhou Yuqi and Min Xinrou's,

00:14:23.740 --> 00:14:24.860 line:80%
for all its shamelessness,

00:14:26.740 --> 00:14:28.330 line:80%
is better than a forced marriage.

00:14:31.380 --> 00:14:32.220 line:80%
Father.

00:14:32.500 --> 00:14:33.340 line:80%
Uncle.

00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:34.450 line:80%
I've made it clear to him.

00:14:35.020 --> 00:14:36.020 line:80%
From now on,

00:14:38.330 --> 00:14:39.500 line:80%
we're just fellow disciples.

00:14:46.100 --> 00:14:47.220 line:80%
As long as it's clear, it's fine.

00:14:48.050 --> 00:14:49.220 line:80%
Clarifying it is enough.

00:14:49.620 --> 00:14:50.460 line:80%
Yunke.

00:14:50.980 --> 00:14:52.220 line:80%
Why not take this chance

00:14:52.570 --> 00:14:54.050 line:80%
to change their engagements?

00:14:56.860 --> 00:14:58.290 line:80%
Nie Zhe is on the run.

00:14:59.100 --> 00:15:00.290 line:80%
Zhao is missing.

00:15:01.290 --> 00:15:02.780 line:80%
I truly have no mind for this.

00:15:04.500 --> 00:15:05.570 line:80%
Let's go to Taichu Temple first.

00:15:24.500 --> 00:15:25.380 line:80%
Dalou, you're here.

00:15:26.170 --> 00:15:27.010 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:15:27.220 --> 00:15:28.330 line:80%
I made you ginger soup.

00:15:28.900 --> 00:15:30.020 line:80%
The weather is getting cold,

00:15:30.220 --> 00:15:31.220 line:80%
be careful of the cold.

00:15:40.330 --> 00:15:41.810 line:80%
Your master
went down the mountain again?

00:15:43.100 --> 00:15:44.530 line:80%
Master went to handle Zhao's matter.

00:15:49.740 --> 00:15:52.140 line:80%
How long have you been on the mountain?

00:15:53.530 --> 00:15:54.370 line:80%
Twenty years.

00:15:56.290 --> 00:15:57.500 line:80%
Twenty years.

00:15:58.900 --> 00:16:01.410 line:80%
Lingbo wasn't even born then.

00:16:03.450 --> 00:16:04.980 line:80%
Lingbo is braver than me.

00:16:07.170 --> 00:16:09.100 line:80%
If I had her courage back then,

00:16:10.290 --> 00:16:11.450 line:80%
I wouldn't be like this now.

00:16:15.930 --> 00:16:16.770 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:16:17.290 --> 00:16:18.650 line:80%
Master has always kept you in his heart.

00:16:19.380 --> 00:16:20.530 line:80%
But he's stuck with trivial matters

00:16:21.410 --> 00:16:22.530 line:80%
and has to mediate.

00:16:25.050 --> 00:16:26.020 line:80%
Maybe.

00:17:02.620 --> 00:17:03.780 line:80%
Gentle wind, light rain.

00:17:04.660 --> 00:17:05.780 line:80%
Smoke from cottages.

00:17:06.370 --> 00:17:08.090 line:80%
Spending the rest of my life here

00:17:08.780 --> 00:17:09.620 line:80%
wouldn't be bad.

00:17:10.030 --> 00:17:11.290 line:80%
You're not going to catch the culprit?

00:17:11.810 --> 00:17:12.650 line:80%
Zhao.

00:17:13.890 --> 00:17:15.700 line:80%
Do you really want me to keep digging?

00:17:17.700 --> 00:17:18.660 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:17:21.020 --> 00:17:22.500 line:80%
The sword formation used by

00:17:22.980 --> 00:17:24.130 line:80%
the Man in Black who ambushed us.

00:17:24.940 --> 00:17:26.570 line:80%
Doesn't it feel familiar to you?

00:17:33.290 --> 00:17:34.370 line:80%
Not the Xuantian Sword Formation.

00:17:35.050 --> 00:17:36.570 line:80%
Just somewhat similar.

00:17:36.570 --> 00:17:38.500 line:80%
Both originate from
the Big Dipper's footwork,

00:17:39.370 --> 00:17:41.500 line:80%
but are fundamentally different.

00:17:41.500 --> 00:17:42.570 line:80%
The leader's

00:17:43.660 --> 00:17:44.500 line:80%
sword techniques.

00:17:48.180 --> 00:17:49.530 line:80%
Definitely not from Qingque Sect.

00:17:51.180 --> 00:17:52.020 line:80%
Dinner's ready,

00:17:54.030 --> 00:17:54.910 line:80%
Uncle Tieqiao.

00:17:54.910 --> 00:17:56.180 line:80%
Time to eat.

00:17:56.180 --> 00:17:57.050 line:80%
You've worked hard.

00:17:57.070 --> 00:17:57.940 line:80%
This is your favorite.

00:18:01.290 --> 00:18:03.180 line:80%
These days the dishes are mostly light.

00:18:03.570 --> 00:18:05.290 line:80%
Why so much meat and fish today?

00:18:05.780 --> 00:18:08.660 line:80%
Well, Mu's injury is almost healed.

00:18:08.660 --> 00:18:11.700 line:80%
Consider this your farewell dinner.

00:18:15.530 --> 00:18:16.370 line:80%
Come on.

00:18:17.180 --> 00:18:18.050 line:80%
Eat more meat.

00:18:19.980 --> 00:18:21.330 line:80%
Uncle Tieqiao, you have some too.

00:18:23.090 --> 00:18:25.500 line:80%
I know why you came here.

00:18:26.420 --> 00:18:27.330 line:80%
Once it's said,

00:18:27.570 --> 00:18:28.570 line:80%
it's time for you to leave.

00:18:29.500 --> 00:18:30.740 line:80%
Lu Chengnan was seriously injured

00:18:32.130 --> 00:18:32.970 line:80%
and

00:18:33.850 --> 00:18:35.180 line:80%
fled to Chang Fort

00:18:35.700 --> 00:18:36.810 line:80%
with Mu Zhengming's help.

00:18:37.180 --> 00:18:38.610 line:80%
Before my father was wounded,

00:18:39.090 --> 00:18:40.530 line:80%
he did rescue many in secret.

00:18:41.020 --> 00:18:42.500 line:80%
Mr. Mu is a good man.

00:18:43.290 --> 00:18:44.130 line:80%
Unfortunately,

00:18:44.940 --> 00:18:47.220 line:80%
Haosheng immediately
sent a carrier pigeon to Pingshu.

00:18:47.220 --> 00:18:49.330 line:80%
We brothers were with her,

00:18:49.660 --> 00:18:50.940 line:80%
so we rushed to Chang clan at once.

00:18:51.780 --> 00:18:52.620 line:80%
By then,

00:18:52.840 --> 00:18:54.330 line:80%
Lu Chengnan's heart meridians
were shattered.

00:18:54.940 --> 00:18:55.890 line:80%
On his deathbed.

00:18:55.890 --> 00:18:57.540 line:80%
(Li Sect, Lu Chengnan)

00:18:58.050 --> 00:18:59.660 line:80%
Why give the Jade Sunflower to me?

00:19:00.500 --> 00:19:01.570 line:80%
My master's skills

00:19:02.290 --> 00:19:03.370 line:80%
reached perfection

00:19:03.850 --> 00:19:05.220 line:80%
years ago.

00:19:06.130 --> 00:19:07.090 line:80%
At his age,

00:19:07.890 --> 00:19:09.290 line:80%
he shouldn't have improved much.

00:19:10.180 --> 00:19:11.220 line:80%
But this year,

00:19:12.980 --> 00:19:16.460 line:80%
I noticed his power surged dramatically.

00:19:17.050 --> 00:19:18.330 line:80%
Secretly, master

00:19:18.330 --> 00:19:19.500 line:80%
ordered Nie clan's disciples

00:19:20.050 --> 00:19:22.220 line:80%
to massacre
many upright martial artists.

00:19:22.660 --> 00:19:24.180 line:80%
They even captured many people alive.

00:19:25.180 --> 00:19:26.460 line:80%
Soon after, what were thrown out

00:19:27.610 --> 00:19:28.890 line:80%
were bodies upon bodies,

00:19:29.780 --> 00:19:31.050 line:80%
dried and lifeless.

00:19:31.850 --> 00:19:33.570 line:80%
All had broken meridians,

00:19:34.330 --> 00:19:35.530 line:80%
destroyed dantians.

00:19:36.050 --> 00:19:37.850 line:80%
All the essence and vital energy
in their body

00:19:38.290 --> 00:19:39.890 line:80%
were completely drained away.

00:19:40.570 --> 00:19:41.530 line:80%
Only then did I realize

00:19:42.740 --> 00:19:44.610 line:80%
my master
had been cultivating our sect's

00:19:45.460 --> 00:19:48.530 line:80%
lost supreme skill,

00:19:49.020 --> 00:19:50.180 line:80%
Ziwei Method.

00:19:50.850 --> 00:19:52.660 line:80%
It requires the Jade Sunflower

00:19:52.660 --> 00:19:55.370 line:80%
to absorb others'
danyuan and inner power.

00:19:55.740 --> 00:19:56.940 line:80%
No wonder many top martial artists

00:19:56.940 --> 00:19:59.700 line:80%
have disappeared
without a trace in recent years.

00:20:00.570 --> 00:20:01.660 line:80%
But gradually,

00:20:02.530 --> 00:20:05.570 line:80%
my master's mind became abnormal.

00:20:06.500 --> 00:20:07.700 line:80%
Sometimes insane.

00:20:09.370 --> 00:20:13.530 line:80%
He even targeted our sect's top experts.

00:20:13.850 --> 00:20:15.020 line:80%
If this continues,

00:20:15.810 --> 00:20:18.290 line:80%
not only will our sect brothers
be slaughtered,

00:20:18.940 --> 00:20:22.330 line:80%
master will also
go mad from cultivation.

00:20:22.610 --> 00:20:24.460 line:80%
So you stole the Jade Sunflower

00:20:24.460 --> 00:20:26.330 line:80%
to stop your master,

00:20:26.330 --> 00:20:27.500 line:80%
make him turn back.

00:20:28.050 --> 00:20:29.290 line:80%
Even though I and Ms. Cai

00:20:29.780 --> 00:20:31.290 line:80%
have never met,

00:20:31.290 --> 00:20:33.130 line:80%
I've long admired you.

00:20:34.220 --> 00:20:35.610 line:80%
You act boldly

00:20:35.980 --> 00:20:37.050 line:80%
and with integrity.

00:20:37.460 --> 00:20:38.810 line:80%
Far better than those

00:20:39.500 --> 00:20:41.180 line:80%
rigid,

00:20:41.180 --> 00:20:42.940 line:80%
selfish old folks.

00:20:43.810 --> 00:20:44.660 line:80%
The future

00:20:45.130 --> 00:20:46.530 line:80%
of the world

00:20:47.500 --> 00:20:48.570 line:80%
is in your hands

00:20:49.700 --> 00:20:50.850 line:80%
to decide.

00:20:59.780 --> 00:21:00.980 line:80%
True friendship

00:21:01.890 --> 00:21:02.980 line:80%
is worth trusting with life.

00:21:04.290 --> 00:21:06.290 line:80%
Aunt and Lu Chengnan are both heroes.

00:21:06.890 --> 00:21:07.730 line:80%
Sadly,

00:21:09.330 --> 00:21:10.610 line:80%
heroes never live long.

00:21:11.330 --> 00:21:12.530 line:80%
Better to be like me.

00:21:12.890 --> 00:21:13.780 line:80%
Care about nothing

00:21:14.130 --> 00:21:15.330 line:80%
and live freely.

00:21:16.610 --> 00:21:17.740 line:80%
So

00:21:18.530 --> 00:21:19.610 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower

00:21:20.090 --> 00:21:21.700 line:80%
is still with Ms. Cai's.

00:21:21.700 --> 00:21:23.090 line:80%
But my parents said

00:21:23.980 --> 00:21:25.890 line:80%
there's no trace of it
in Luoying Valley.

00:21:26.610 --> 00:21:27.890 line:80%
Pingshu once said

00:21:28.330 --> 00:21:31.220 line:80%
this thing is a curse.

00:21:31.940 --> 00:21:33.500 line:80%
You're both so young,

00:21:34.740 --> 00:21:35.610 line:80%
if you can't find it,

00:21:36.530 --> 00:21:38.570 line:80%
better give up.

00:21:38.940 --> 00:21:39.890 line:80%
Don't let this

00:21:40.940 --> 00:21:41.810 line:80%
cause more trouble.

00:21:45.780 --> 00:21:46.620 line:80%
Fine,

00:21:47.090 --> 00:21:49.460 line:80%
maybe it's all aunt's will from heaven.

00:21:49.890 --> 00:21:50.730 line:80%
Senior,

00:21:51.370 --> 00:21:52.570 line:80%
what exactly does

00:21:53.020 --> 00:21:54.130 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower look like?

00:21:54.570 --> 00:21:56.330 line:80%
It was burned

00:21:57.530 --> 00:21:58.570 line:80%
in the Li Sect treasury.

00:21:58.810 --> 00:21:59.980 line:80%
Only left with…

00:22:11.020 --> 00:22:12.050 line:80%
Since it's a curse,

00:22:13.940 --> 00:22:14.780 line:80%
why cling to it?

00:22:16.660 --> 00:22:17.500 line:80%
Tieqiao.

00:22:18.660 --> 00:22:19.850 line:80%
Hurry, come see Zigui with me.

00:22:20.700 --> 00:22:21.850 line:80%
Zigui has awakened?

00:22:21.850 --> 00:22:22.940 line:80%
It must be time.

00:22:24.220 --> 00:22:25.530 line:80%
The Shi twins

00:22:25.530 --> 00:22:26.570 line:80%
have Zigui?

00:22:26.570 --> 00:22:27.660 line:80%
Zigui

00:22:27.660 --> 00:22:28.570 line:80%
has been comatose for years.

00:22:29.180 --> 00:22:30.090 line:80%
Now he's awake.

00:22:31.020 --> 00:22:32.130 line:80%
It must be fate.

00:22:32.570 --> 00:22:33.460 line:80%
You two.

00:22:33.460 --> 00:22:34.330 line:80%
Come with me.

00:22:35.180 --> 00:22:36.020 line:80%
Let's go.

00:23:00.290 --> 00:23:01.420 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:23:04.460 --> 00:23:05.460 line:80%
She is not Pingshu.

00:23:05.940 --> 00:23:07.740 line:80%
She's the daughter
of Xiaofeng and Pingchun.

00:23:07.740 --> 00:23:08.580 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:23:13.890 --> 00:23:14.740 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:23:15.490 --> 00:23:16.330 line:80%
Yes.

00:23:16.330 --> 00:23:19.020 line:80%
She's also a disciple of Yunke.

00:23:19.500 --> 00:23:20.780 line:80%
Xiaofeng and

00:23:20.780 --> 00:23:23.050 line:80%
Pingchun's daughter.

00:23:23.460 --> 00:23:25.330 line:80%
She's grown up so much.

00:23:25.980 --> 00:23:27.180 line:80%
Back then, we promised

00:23:27.740 --> 00:23:29.530 line:80%
to carry Xiaofeng

00:23:29.530 --> 00:23:30.420 line:80%
at her wedding.

00:23:31.220 --> 00:23:33.130 line:80%
But I broke my word.

00:23:34.220 --> 00:23:35.090 line:80%
Zhao.

00:23:35.530 --> 00:23:36.370 line:80%
How's

00:23:37.020 --> 00:23:38.570 line:80%
your mother?

00:23:40.700 --> 00:23:41.780 line:80%
My mother is fine.

00:23:42.290 --> 00:23:43.330 line:80%
And you are...

00:23:43.610 --> 00:23:45.610 line:80%
You must be Yin Dai's seventh disciple.

00:23:46.220 --> 00:23:47.060 line:80%
Guo Zigui.

00:23:48.780 --> 00:23:50.660 line:80%
Who is Uncle Guo?

00:23:50.660 --> 00:23:53.500 line:80%
He's the uncle
who grew up with your mother.

00:23:53.500 --> 00:23:55.420 line:80%
And also my and your Uncle Qi's
junior brother.

00:23:56.420 --> 00:23:57.570 line:80%
How could that be?

00:23:58.460 --> 00:23:59.530 line:80%
Uncle Guo

00:23:59.980 --> 00:24:01.420 line:80%
is the same age as my mother.

00:24:02.290 --> 00:24:03.500 line:80%
Your Uncle Guo

00:24:03.500 --> 00:24:05.610 line:80%
was born into
a wealthy family in Jiangdong.

00:24:05.610 --> 00:24:08.290 line:80%
A charmer by the bridge at dusk.

00:24:08.940 --> 00:24:11.050 line:80%
He idled all day.

00:24:11.700 --> 00:24:13.220 line:80%
A laughing

00:24:13.220 --> 00:24:14.220 line:80%
and cheerful lad.

00:24:15.330 --> 00:24:18.700 line:80%
Your maternal grandparents'home was
just one alley away from the Guo clan's.

00:24:18.700 --> 00:24:20.530 line:80%
Whenever your mother met Zigui,

00:24:20.530 --> 00:24:23.570 line:80%
it was bound to
stir trouble and headaches for all.

00:24:23.570 --> 00:24:25.220 line:80%
We were childhood sweethearts,

00:24:25.220 --> 00:24:26.520 line:80%
as close as siblings.

00:24:26.530 --> 00:24:27.790 line:80%
As close as siblings.

00:24:32.020 --> 00:24:32.980 line:80%
Uncle Guo.

00:24:33.590 --> 00:24:34.980 line:80%
(Qingque Sect, Guo Zigui)
Mom has been looking for you.

00:24:35.610 --> 00:24:36.940 line:80%
Why haven't you come back?

00:24:37.500 --> 00:24:38.340 line:80%
Xiaofeng

00:24:38.810 --> 00:24:41.220 line:80%
must want me to join in her games.

00:24:42.290 --> 00:24:43.130 line:80%
Kid.

00:24:43.850 --> 00:24:45.810 line:80%
How is your aunt?

00:24:47.020 --> 00:24:48.180 line:80%
My aunt, she...

00:24:56.290 --> 00:24:57.850 line:80%
She's at Luoying Valley.

00:24:58.460 --> 00:24:59.500 line:80%
She's in poor health,

00:25:00.290 --> 00:25:01.980 line:80%
resting there to recover.

00:25:02.980 --> 00:25:04.180 line:80%
Resting is good.

00:25:04.700 --> 00:25:05.890 line:80%
Your aunt…

00:25:06.940 --> 00:25:09.220 line:80%
has suffered too much.

00:25:11.460 --> 00:25:12.300 line:80%
Zhao.

00:25:12.740 --> 00:25:14.220 line:80%
Tell me.

00:25:14.890 --> 00:25:16.290 line:80%
How are things in the sect?

00:25:16.980 --> 00:25:18.330 line:80%
Come, help me up.

00:25:18.890 --> 00:25:19.730 line:80%
Alright.

00:25:22.570 --> 00:25:23.410 line:80%
Sit down.

00:25:25.660 --> 00:25:26.780 line:80%
Qingque Sect.

00:25:28.980 --> 00:25:30.290 line:80%
How is it now?

00:25:30.290 --> 00:25:31.370 line:80%
Everything's good

00:25:32.420 --> 00:25:33.570 line:80%
except the cook isn't great.

00:25:34.250 --> 00:25:35.130 line:80%
You know

00:25:35.130 --> 00:25:36.020 line:80%
my master's personality.

00:25:36.460 --> 00:25:37.570 line:80%
Lenient with himself.

00:25:37.570 --> 00:25:38.980 line:80%
Even more so with others.

00:25:38.980 --> 00:25:41.050 line:80%
So now at Qingque Sect,

00:25:41.050 --> 00:25:42.050 line:80%
everyone

00:25:42.050 --> 00:25:44.420 line:80%
loves gathering
to chat.

00:25:44.420 --> 00:25:46.180 line:80%
The sunflower seed shells
they crack each day

00:25:46.180 --> 00:25:48.020 line:80%
can pile up into a big basket.

00:25:48.810 --> 00:25:50.530 line:80%
Luckily Uncle Li Wenxun is there,

00:25:50.530 --> 00:25:51.980 line:80%
so the sect rules still hold firm.

00:25:55.220 --> 00:25:56.500 line:80%
Not like

00:25:58.180 --> 00:25:59.180 line:80%
back in our day.

00:25:59.810 --> 00:26:00.700 line:80%
But

00:26:01.460 --> 00:26:03.090 line:80%
so many senior brothers

00:26:03.500 --> 00:26:04.700 line:80%
are gone.

00:26:05.530 --> 00:26:06.850 line:80%
Uncle Lei is still around.

00:26:06.850 --> 00:26:08.890 line:80%
He loves rambling about pill quality

00:26:09.090 --> 00:26:10.530 line:80%
in the Herb Hut.

00:26:11.330 --> 00:26:12.340 line:80%
He's someone

00:26:14.890 --> 00:26:16.020 line:80%
who loves looking good.

00:26:17.810 --> 00:26:19.700 line:80%
Once he's dressed up,

00:26:20.810 --> 00:26:22.980 line:80%
he likes going where it's crowded.

00:26:24.940 --> 00:26:27.810 line:80%
Now he stays in the Herb Hut all day.

00:26:28.220 --> 00:26:30.180 line:80%
He must be wounded.

00:26:31.460 --> 00:26:34.610 line:80%
Just a few small scars on his face.

00:26:35.810 --> 00:26:36.810 line:80%
I don't think it's a big deal.

00:26:37.290 --> 00:26:38.740 line:80%
I think it makes him look more valiant.

00:26:39.180 --> 00:26:40.740 line:80%
If it's only a few small scars,

00:26:42.290 --> 00:26:44.020 line:80%
he could heal them himself.

00:26:45.370 --> 00:26:47.370 line:80%
There must be other injuries.

00:26:48.460 --> 00:26:50.700 line:80%
Luckily, he's still alive.

00:26:51.290 --> 00:26:53.230 line:80%
Being alive is enough.

00:26:56.330 --> 00:26:57.170 line:80%
Uncle Guo.

00:26:57.570 --> 00:26:58.410 line:80%
Let me do it.

00:26:59.090 --> 00:26:59.930 line:80%
Let me handle it.

00:27:02.020 --> 00:27:02.860 line:80%
Uncle Guo.

00:27:07.660 --> 00:27:10.020 line:80%
This is clearly
draining Uncle Guo's vitality.

00:27:10.020 --> 00:27:11.420 line:80%
This is trading the future for now.

00:27:11.420 --> 00:27:12.260 line:80%
Zhao.

00:27:13.850 --> 00:27:15.290 line:80%
Zigui's injuries are far too severe.

00:27:15.290 --> 00:27:17.050 line:80%
This is the only way left
to keep him alive.

00:27:40.020 --> 00:27:40.980 line:80%
Zhao.

00:27:42.290 --> 00:27:44.700 line:80%
Bring some things back for me.

00:27:47.890 --> 00:27:49.810 line:80%
Guo clan of Jiangdong

00:27:49.810 --> 00:27:51.660 line:80%
is gone now.

00:27:51.660 --> 00:27:52.740 line:80%
These are my

00:27:55.180 --> 00:27:57.780 line:80%
only remaining belongings.

00:27:58.700 --> 00:28:00.130 line:80%
Consider it

00:28:02.180 --> 00:28:03.810 line:80%
as extra dowry
for your mom.

00:28:08.290 --> 00:28:09.810 line:80%
- And your aunt...
- Zigui.

00:28:14.050 --> 00:28:14.980 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:28:19.940 --> 00:28:20.780 line:80%
Zigui.

00:28:21.050 --> 00:28:21.890 line:80%
I promise.

00:28:22.020 --> 00:28:22.860 line:80%
Next time.

00:28:23.020 --> 00:28:24.610 line:80%
Next time I'll take you to roam Jianghu.

00:28:24.820 --> 00:28:25.700 line:80%
Zigui.

00:28:25.700 --> 00:28:27.370 line:80%
Wait until you've mastered your skills.

00:28:27.660 --> 00:28:29.220 line:80%
We're out to uphold justice.

00:28:29.220 --> 00:28:30.370 line:80%
Not just out for leisure.

00:28:30.980 --> 00:28:32.700 line:80%
With your current clumsy moves,

00:28:32.700 --> 00:28:33.570 line:80%
blood will make you faint.

00:28:33.980 --> 00:28:34.940 line:80%
When the time comes,

00:28:34.940 --> 00:28:36.050 line:80%
we'd have to carry you back.

00:28:39.500 --> 00:28:40.340 line:80%
Zigui.

00:28:40.610 --> 00:28:41.450 line:80%
Master already said,

00:28:41.780 --> 00:28:42.620 line:80%
you've got talent.

00:28:42.980 --> 00:28:43.820 line:80%
You'll master it for sure.

00:28:47.420 --> 00:28:50.090 line:80%
Come on.

00:28:50.090 --> 00:28:51.370 line:80%
- Drink up. Drink up.
- Drink up.

00:28:51.370 --> 00:28:52.290 line:80%
Cheers.

00:28:52.290 --> 00:28:53.130 line:80%
Come on.

00:28:53.890 --> 00:28:54.730 line:80%
Fill it up, fill it up.

00:28:55.090 --> 00:28:55.930 line:80%
Alright.

00:28:56.780 --> 00:28:59.020 line:80%
Zigui, join us for a drink.

00:28:59.500 --> 00:29:01.050 line:80%
Breeze.

00:29:01.420 --> 00:29:02.260 line:80%
- Here!
- Hurry over.

00:29:02.850 --> 00:29:03.940 line:80%
Come on.

00:29:06.420 --> 00:29:08.810 line:80%
- Drink, drink!
- Cheers!

00:29:12.740 --> 00:29:15.290 line:80%
I saw Pingshu raised the Sunshine Blade.

00:29:15.810 --> 00:29:16.780 line:80%
Those bandits were so scared.

00:29:16.780 --> 00:29:18.810 line:80%
And they scrambled away in seconds.

00:29:19.330 --> 00:29:21.660 line:80%
One even fainted on the spot!

00:29:23.940 --> 00:29:25.410 line:80%
Zigui, here.

00:29:26.890 --> 00:29:27.810 line:80%
It hurts, it hurts!

00:29:27.810 --> 00:29:28.780 line:80%
Zigui.

00:29:28.780 --> 00:29:31.020 line:80%
- Scared of pain? Then why learn martial arts?
- Exactly.

00:29:31.020 --> 00:29:33.330 line:80%
Because Lord Yin personally
went to Jiangdong and

00:29:33.330 --> 00:29:34.740 line:80%
insisted on
taking Zigui as his disciple.

00:29:34.740 --> 00:29:35.580 line:80%
Right?

00:29:36.700 --> 00:29:38.660 line:80%
I heard the Mu Wei Palace
was just renovated.

00:29:38.660 --> 00:29:39.700 line:80%
Your family paid for that again.

00:29:40.460 --> 00:29:41.890 line:80%
As disciples of Qingque Sect,

00:29:41.890 --> 00:29:43.850 line:80%
it's only right to serve the sect.

00:29:49.420 --> 00:29:53.500 line:80%
(Lord of Qingque Sect, Yin Dai)

00:29:53.530 --> 00:29:55.500 line:80%
The demon sect has evil ambitions.

00:29:56.570 --> 00:29:57.980 line:80%
Jianghu is in danger.

00:29:59.740 --> 00:30:01.290 line:80%
Disciples of the Six Sects,

00:30:01.700 --> 00:30:03.420 line:80%
you must do your duty

00:30:04.740 --> 00:30:06.290 line:80%
and eliminate the devil!

00:30:06.810 --> 00:30:09.460 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)
Eliminate the devil!

00:30:09.460 --> 00:30:10.370 line:80%
In that battle,

00:30:10.850 --> 00:30:12.660 line:80%
almost all the younger disciples went

00:30:13.500 --> 00:30:16.130 line:80%
except Qiu Yuanfeng,
who was recovering from injuries.

00:30:18.940 --> 00:30:20.290 line:80%
- What are you doing here?
- Pingshu.

00:30:20.290 --> 00:30:21.940 line:80%
Yuanjing, keep Zigui safe.

00:30:21.940 --> 00:30:22.780 line:80%
Okay.

00:30:24.890 --> 00:30:25.940 line:80%
Fight!

00:30:26.850 --> 00:30:28.130 line:80%
Fight!

00:30:39.370 --> 00:30:40.460 line:80%
Zigui, over here.

00:30:47.090 --> 00:30:48.460 line:80%
Wang Yuanjing took Zigui

00:30:49.290 --> 00:30:50.660 line:80%
and got lost in the EightClaw Prison.

00:31:12.780 --> 00:31:14.610 line:80%
They accidentally
separated in the chaos.

00:31:38.500 --> 00:31:39.340 line:80%
Where's Zigui?

00:31:39.810 --> 00:31:41.180 line:80%
I got separated from Zigui.

00:31:41.780 --> 00:31:43.370 line:80%
- I'll go find him.
- I saw him running back.

00:31:43.850 --> 00:31:44.810 line:80%
He must've gone back.

00:31:50.370 --> 00:31:51.780 line:80%
But never returned.

00:31:53.130 --> 00:31:54.370 line:80%
Pingshu snuck into the Youming Path

00:31:55.370 --> 00:31:57.020 line:80%
several times to find him,

00:31:58.090 --> 00:31:59.850 line:80%
but the Hanhai Mountains are too big.

00:32:01.330 --> 00:32:02.460 line:80%
Impossible to locate.

00:32:13.810 --> 00:32:14.650 line:80%
Never thought

00:32:15.330 --> 00:32:16.570 line:80%
he's so tough.

00:32:17.500 --> 00:32:19.370 line:80%
Every bone in his body was crushed,

00:32:20.180 --> 00:32:21.420 line:80%
yet he endured.

00:32:25.570 --> 00:32:26.740 line:80%
I won't surrender.

00:32:28.420 --> 00:32:29.570 line:80%
I won't surrender.

00:32:30.290 --> 00:32:31.130 line:80%
Keep beating him.

00:32:43.540 --> 00:32:44.780 line:80%
(Parents alive, when can I go home?)

00:32:44.780 --> 00:32:45.620 line:80%
Father.

00:32:46.660 --> 00:32:47.500 line:80%
Mother.

00:32:50.090 --> 00:32:51.020 line:80%
It hurts.

00:32:52.020 --> 00:32:52.940 line:80%
It hurts.

00:32:54.020 --> 00:32:54.860 line:80%
Mother.

00:32:55.780 --> 00:32:56.980 line:80%
Take me home.

00:32:58.660 --> 00:32:59.570 line:80%
Take me...

00:32:59.570 --> 00:33:00.660 line:80%
Take me home.

00:33:04.500 --> 00:33:06.090 line:80%
Just sign the surrender letter,

00:33:07.050 --> 00:33:08.700 line:80%
and your master will take you home.

00:33:13.220 --> 00:33:15.220 line:80%
Keep dreaming.

00:33:39.420 --> 00:33:40.260 line:80%
Zigui.

00:33:44.500 --> 00:33:45.340 line:80%
Zigui.

00:33:47.420 --> 00:33:48.290 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:33:48.290 --> 00:33:49.370 line:80%
My son.

00:33:49.370 --> 00:33:50.210 line:80%
Father!

00:33:51.850 --> 00:33:52.850 line:80%
Zigui.

00:33:52.850 --> 00:33:53.690 line:80%
Mother.

00:33:55.660 --> 00:33:56.610 line:80%
Come.

00:33:56.610 --> 00:33:57.500 line:80%
Come home with me.

00:33:58.780 --> 00:33:59.700 line:80%
Come home.

00:34:00.090 --> 00:34:00.930 line:80%
My son.

00:34:01.980 --> 00:34:03.290 line:80%
Come home with me.

00:34:03.290 --> 00:34:04.130 line:80%
Zigui.

00:34:04.700 --> 00:34:05.540 line:80%
Come home with me.

00:34:06.290 --> 00:34:07.180 line:80%
Come home.

00:34:17.620 --> 00:34:18.460 line:80%
Come home.

00:34:18.460 --> 00:34:19.300 line:80%
(Respectfully, Guo Zigui)

00:34:20.930 --> 00:34:21.810 line:80%
Come home.

00:34:24.540 --> 00:34:27.740 line:80%
The demon sect sent Zigui's
surrender letter to Yin Dai.

00:34:28.970 --> 00:34:30.660 line:80%
But Yin Dai refused to save him

00:34:31.890 --> 00:34:33.140 line:80%
and even issued a kill order.

00:34:33.580 --> 00:34:34.740 line:80%
Lord Yin.

00:34:35.580 --> 00:34:37.970 line:80%
As long as you save Zigui,

00:34:37.970 --> 00:34:41.410 line:80%
I'll give you all my family property.

00:34:41.410 --> 00:34:44.290 line:80%
Please save Zigui.

00:34:44.290 --> 00:34:46.740 line:80%
Such a cowardly man

00:34:46.740 --> 00:34:48.140 line:80%
deserves to die to prove his loyalty!

00:34:48.930 --> 00:34:49.780 line:80%
No.

00:34:49.780 --> 00:34:51.780 line:80%
- Please, Lord Yin!
- Mr. Guo, Mrs. Guo.

00:34:52.660 --> 00:34:53.500 line:80%
Lord Yin.

00:34:53.700 --> 00:34:55.660 line:80%
Zigui is Beichen disciple.
Why not save him?

00:34:55.890 --> 00:34:57.180 line:80%
Any Qingque Sect disciple

00:34:57.850 --> 00:35:00.620 line:80%
who shows weakness
and surrenders to the enemy

00:35:00.620 --> 00:35:01.970 line:80%
deserves death.

00:35:01.970 --> 00:35:03.810 line:80%
I'm being lenient

00:35:04.220 --> 00:35:05.810 line:80%
by not killing him myself.

00:35:05.810 --> 00:35:06.850 line:80%
He never hurt anyone!

00:35:06.860 --> 00:35:07.730 line:80%
In this world,

00:35:07.730 --> 00:35:09.370 line:80%
not everyone is born a hero.

00:35:09.370 --> 00:35:12.850 line:80%
If everyone is cowardly
and surrenders easily,

00:35:13.290 --> 00:35:15.290 line:80%
what's left of loyalty
and righteousness?

00:35:15.490 --> 00:35:18.290 line:80%
How can the Six Sects of Beichen
command respect?

00:35:18.620 --> 00:35:19.740 line:80%
Is it really wrong to fear death?

00:35:20.290 --> 00:35:21.140 line:80%
Wasn't the reason we

00:35:21.140 --> 00:35:23.450 line:80%
learned martial arts
to rid the world of bullying

00:35:23.450 --> 00:35:25.010 line:80%
and unnecessary sacrifice?

00:35:26.220 --> 00:35:27.490 line:80%
Words mean nothing now.

00:35:28.490 --> 00:35:29.330 line:80%
No one from the Six Sects

00:35:29.970 --> 00:35:31.140 line:80%
will save him.

00:35:31.740 --> 00:35:32.740 line:80%
Whoever does

00:35:33.660 --> 00:35:35.290 line:80%
is deemed a traitor.

00:35:36.490 --> 00:35:37.330 line:80%
Later,

00:35:38.330 --> 00:35:39.700 line:80%
Pingshu searched for a long time

00:35:40.930 --> 00:35:42.140 line:80%
and finally found out

00:35:43.620 --> 00:35:46.930 line:80%
Zigui was locked
in the EightClaw Prison.

00:35:50.780 --> 00:35:51.620 line:80%
Zigui.

00:35:53.620 --> 00:35:54.490 line:80%
Don't beat me.

00:35:54.660 --> 00:35:55.700 line:80%
Don't beat me.

00:35:56.580 --> 00:35:57.420 line:80%
It hurts.

00:35:58.330 --> 00:35:59.930 line:80%
No... Don't hit me.

00:36:00.660 --> 00:36:01.500 line:80%
Zigui.

00:36:02.180 --> 00:36:03.100 line:80%
It's me, Pingshu.

00:36:11.780 --> 00:36:12.620 line:80%
Senior Sister.

00:36:13.180 --> 00:36:14.020 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:36:15.490 --> 00:36:16.540 line:80%
I'm taking you home.

00:36:17.780 --> 00:36:18.620 line:80%
Home.

00:36:20.540 --> 00:36:22.450 line:80%
Home.

00:36:26.700 --> 00:36:27.740 line:80%
Home.

00:36:32.010 --> 00:36:34.010 line:80%
- Home...
- Sadly, the two elders of the Guo clan

00:36:35.540 --> 00:36:37.580 line:80%
never got the chance
to see their son again.

00:36:39.100 --> 00:36:41.140 line:80%
Not long after
returning from Qingque Sect,

00:36:42.450 --> 00:36:43.740 line:80%
they both

00:36:45.780 --> 00:36:47.010 line:80%
died of anger.

00:36:56.970 --> 00:36:58.890 line:80%
Let Zigui retire with you.

00:36:59.390 --> 00:37:00.850 line:80%
He never wanted
anything to do with Jianghu.

00:37:01.620 --> 00:37:02.460 line:80%
Staying here.

00:37:02.850 --> 00:37:04.010 line:80%
A few years of peace, at least.

00:37:04.290 --> 00:37:05.130 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:37:05.290 --> 00:37:06.290 line:80%
You retire too.

00:37:06.890 --> 00:37:07.730 line:80%
This world...

00:37:09.010 --> 00:37:10.740 line:80%
isn't what we imagined.

00:37:10.740 --> 00:37:12.740 line:80%
Then let's make it into
what we imagined.

00:37:12.740 --> 00:37:14.020 line:80%
- Pingshu, you...
- Tieqiao.

00:37:14.580 --> 00:37:15.780 line:80%
Someone has to hold on.

00:37:41.100 --> 00:37:42.450 line:80%
Pingshu!

00:37:43.780 --> 00:37:44.620 line:80%
Zigui.

00:37:47.370 --> 00:37:49.580 line:80%
Pingshu!

00:38:39.540 --> 00:38:40.380 line:80%
Let me do it.

00:38:42.290 --> 00:38:43.180 line:80%
Uncle Guo.

00:39:02.140 --> 00:39:03.100 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:39:04.780 --> 00:39:05.710 line:80%
- Father.
- Try this.

00:39:07.020 --> 00:39:08.020 line:80%
- Mother.
- This one is nice.

00:39:09.100 --> 00:39:10.410 line:80%
- Zigui, come drink.
- Have a taste.

00:39:11.370 --> 00:39:12.580 line:80%
Breeze!

00:39:30.330 --> 00:39:31.450 line:80%
Chang.

00:39:31.450 --> 00:39:32.330 line:80%
Come.

00:39:32.330 --> 00:39:33.290 line:80%
Shi.

00:39:34.810 --> 00:39:35.650 line:80%
Wu.

00:39:35.970 --> 00:39:36.810 line:80%
Zigui.

00:39:37.330 --> 00:39:38.290 line:80%
Yuanrong.

00:39:40.010 --> 00:39:40.850 line:80%
Qi.

00:39:42.540 --> 00:39:43.380 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:39:45.620 --> 00:39:46.780 line:80%
Xiaofeng.

00:39:46.780 --> 00:39:47.620 line:80%
Zigui.

00:39:48.780 --> 00:39:49.620 line:80%
Father.

00:39:49.890 --> 00:39:50.730 line:80%
Mother.

00:39:51.780 --> 00:39:52.620 line:80%
Son.

00:39:58.220 --> 00:39:59.490 line:80%
My good son.

00:40:01.010 --> 00:40:02.100 line:80%
Come, let me take a look.

00:40:03.620 --> 00:40:04.740 line:80%
You've grown much stronger.

00:40:14.490 --> 00:40:15.410 line:80%
Come on, let's drink.

00:40:15.780 --> 00:40:17.850 line:80%
Come on, fill every cup, let's drink.

00:40:21.290 --> 00:40:23.810 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle♪

00:40:23.810 --> 00:40:26.180 line:80%
♪And spring is fair♪

00:40:26.490 --> 00:40:28.870 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills♪

00:40:28.870 --> 00:40:31.300 line:80%
♪In the martial world♪

00:40:31.540 --> 00:40:34.000 line:80%
♪With a shining cup♪

00:40:34.000 --> 00:40:36.140 line:80%
♪I drink with delight tonight♪

00:40:36.550 --> 00:40:37.840 line:80%
♪Free to wander♪

00:40:37.840 --> 00:40:40.260 line:80%
♪in the world♪

00:40:40.280 --> 00:40:41.370 line:80%
Till we're drunk!

00:40:41.370 --> 00:40:43.290 line:80%
Till we're done!

00:40:43.290 --> 00:40:44.290 line:80%
Cheers!

00:40:44.290 --> 00:40:48.590 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:40:48.880 --> 00:40:53.380 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:40:53.970 --> 00:40:58.140 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:40:58.370 --> 00:41:03.520 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:41:03.960 --> 00:41:08.880 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:09.080 --> 00:41:13.330 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
